title: Warriors Come Out And Play.  Pusha T and Drizzy.  Slurred Lines With J. Anthony Brown.  WNBA, Sand and Soul, Closing Remarks and more.

description:
Warriors take Game 1 of NBA Finals. Pusha T and Drizzy got beef. Fool #2 hits Roseanne with Slurred Lines. WNBA President Lisa Borders stops by. Sand and Soul II is on its way. Today in the Closing Remarks, The CEO talks about Life and Death and more!
